title: Outstanding Note Circulation, All Banks for Germany
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1875-1913 (2)--Original Data, 1914-1934. Data For 1914-1922 Cover Nineteen Banks; Coverage Thereafter Is Of The Reichsbank And Four Private Note-Issuing State Banks. Data Are At The End Of Month. Source: Reichsamt Des Innern, Ministerialblatt, Centralblatt, 1876 And Following Years; Also See Wirtschaft Und Statistik.

This NBER data series m14088b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 14 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter14.html.
